---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="The Quorum | Agora" description="The strategic and theoretical core of the Agora movement.">
  
  <article class="pt-32 pb-24 px-6 text-zinc-100 antialiased">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-16">
      
      <header class="space-y-6">
        <div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-white/20 text-[10px] font-mono uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-white">
          Internal Governance
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold tracking-tight">Quorum</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed font-serif italic">
          “A movement without a theory is a movement that can be bought.”
        </p>
      </header>

      <hr class="border-zinc-800" />

      <section class="space-y-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">What is Quorum?</h2>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
          If you’re a member of Agora has proven your reliability, responsability, and dedication to our community, your sponsor may recommend you as a new member of the Quorum. This is the name we use to refer to Agora’s core organizers and leadership. As a member of Quorum, you’ll have more responsabilities, but you’ll also have the right to vote on the leadership and direction of our movement.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">The Strategic Compass</h2>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
          While Agora is distributed at the chapter level, the <strong>Quorum</strong> serves as the movement’s central nervous system. This inner core of organizers is responsible for the long-term survival of the project, ensuring that our decentralized nature does not lead to drift or fragmentation.
        </p>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
          The Quorum is not a ruling body, but a <strong>theoretical vanguard</strong>. Their authority is derived from their responsibility to the Manifesto.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="grid gap-8">
        <div class="p-8 bg-zinc-900 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 space-y-4">
          <h3 class="text-white font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-xs">01. Political Education</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Developing the curriculum for Chapter Leaders and Sponsors. The Quorum distills complex critiques of neoliberalism into actionable knowledge for the community.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-8 bg-zinc-900 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 space-y-4">
          <h3 class="text-white font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-xs">02. Campaign Strategy</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Identifying systemic targets for offline action. The Quorum coordinates national and global “days of exit” to maximize the movement's visibility and impact.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-8 bg-zinc-900 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 space-y-4">
          <h3 class="text-white font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-xs">03. Project Integrity</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Maintaining the app infrastructure. The Quorum manages the code and data of the app, ensuring it remains a utility for members rather than a product for markets.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-6 pt-12 border-t border-zinc-800">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">How the Quorum Forms</h2>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
          Entry into the Quorum is not through election, but through <strong>proven stewardship</strong>. It is composed of the movement's most active organizers who have successfully built and sustained local chapters for a period of no less than two years.
        </p>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-tight text-zinc-500">
          Status: Active // Members: Undisclosed for security
        </p>
      </section>

      <footer class="pt-12">
        <a href="/philosophy" class="text-white hover:text-zinc-400 transition flex items-center gap-2">
          ← Back to Philosophy
        </a>
      </footer>

    </div>
  </article>

</Layout>